channel.title: Tos-Scape v4
channel.description:
Hi, Some people might remember Tos-Scape (guess no-one will). Anyway, I basicly stopped coding since march or something (due to gf's, social life, musical career, ...). But I'm bored as hell now, so I'd like to pick up again and start a Tos-Scape v4. I'm not realy recruiting.. It's more like bringing people back who helped me with the v1, v2 & v3. Unless you really want to help, or focus on a project, let me know (This thread, PM, Msn, ...) IF so: - I want creative people (Idea's) - You don't necesairly need to be experienced - You DO need to have some basic java knowledge
Greetings
* If you want I can repost my Tos-Scape download lol *
